ğŸ§¾ Deliverable: Red Team Report + attack chain diagram + risk scoring + recommendations

ğŸ” Optional: Conduct a blue team debrief (purple team mode), to improve defenses.

ğŸ”„ 7. Purple Team Engagement (Optional)
